          "summary": "Fern helps engineering teams build APIs twice as fast. Define your API in OpenAPI or in Fern’s simpler format. Fern generates types, networking code and SDKs, and handles publishing SDKs to registries like npm, integrates with Postman, and syncs with documentation websites like ReadMe and Stoplight. Learn more",
